greater the prayer covering, the greater

00:11:59.200 --> 00:12:01.509
the glory will manifest. This is why

00:12:01.519 --> 00:12:06.629
there'll be much migration with

00:12:06.639 --> 00:12:09.590
churches in the days ahead. He said it

00:12:09.600 --> 00:12:13.110
will not be considered equal everywhere.

00:12:13.120 --> 00:12:15.750
The greater the prayer, the greater the

00:12:15.760 --> 00:12:18.150
glory. The greater the manifestation of

00:12:18.160 --> 00:12:20.870
intercessory prayer over that area, the

00:12:20.880 --> 00:12:22.790
greater the manifestations of the glory

00:12:22.800 --> 00:12:25.670
over that area. And he said, 'This is

00:12:25.680 --> 00:12:30.230
why Tulsa, Oklahoma will be a hot spot

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:33.670
because there are great wells of prayer

00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:35.990
that are still there from even the

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:37.990
elders that know how to pray—from the

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:41.269
Kenneth Hagin, the

00:12:41.269 --> 00:12:41.279
Hagins, and Oral

00:12:41.279 --> 00:12:44.310
Roberts and so

00:12:44.310 --> 00:12:44.320
on—from

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:48.150
all of the great revival and

00:12:48.160 --> 00:12:50.870
word-based, faith-based prayer that have

00:12:50.880 --> 00:12:54.389
been here since the 70s and

00:12:54.399 --> 00:12:56.629
before, right from Oral Roberts

00:12:56.639 --> 00:12:58.310
University and all that.'And that's what

00:12:58.320 --> 00:13:00.470
the Lord was saying: you'll see mass

00:13:00.480 --> 00:13:03.350
migration of Christians in the days

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:05.670
ahead, for great revival will come where

00:13:05.680 --> 00:13:07.750
there's great prayer. That's why it was

00:13:07.760 --> 00:13:09.750
in Tennessee.

00:13:09.760 --> 00:13:12.150
That's why it's around Mobile, I believe,

00:13:12.160 --> 00:13:15.750
with

00:13:15.760 --> 00:13:18.470
Pastor John Kilpatrick

00:13:18.470 --> 00:13:18.480
in

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:19.110
Alabama.

00:13:22.160 --> 00:13:25.990
I believe it's Bill, but they know

00:13:26.000 --> 00:13:28.069
how to pray

00:13:28.079 --> 00:13:34.150
and revival begins with prayer.

00:13:34.160 --> 00:13:36.550
Everything is always cultivated with

00:13:36.560 --> 00:13:38.949
prayer. And that's why this channel

00:13:38.959 --> 00:13:40.710
exists:

00:13:40.720 --> 00:13:42.470
prayer, prayer, prayer.

00:13:42.480 --> 00:13:44.150
Foundation. And it was neat yesterday

00:13:44.160 --> 00:13:46.150
when I saw Jesus in that vision as I was walking,

00:13:46.160 --> 00:13:48.150
and his

00:13:48.160 --> 00:13:51.430
foot in prayer was making indentations in

00:13:51.440 --> 00:13:54.069
the spirit realm as we were walking, not

00:13:54.079 --> 00:13:57.189
behind him, but beside him as a child

00:13:57.199 --> 00:13:59.910
would their father.

00:13:59.920 --> 00:14:01.829
We don't look at ourselves as

00:14:01.839 --> 00:14:04.870
broken and humble like, 'Oh Lord,

00:14:04.880 --> 00:14:06.949
we're humble and we're

00:14:06.949 --> 00:14:06.959
broken,'but

00:14:06.959 --> 00:14:10.310
we're joint-heirs with Jesus.

00:14:10.320 --> 00:14:12.550
Don't act like, 'Oh, I'm beat down, I'm a

00:14:12.550 --> 00:14:12.560
child.'No,

00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:15.509
I'm like, 'Oh, Daddy, how are you doing

00:14:15.519 --> 00:14:19.350
today? Let me tell you about my

00:14:19.360 --> 00:14:21.590
day,

00:14:21.590 --> 00:14:21.600
Father.''Oh,

00:14:21.600 --> 00:14:24.150
tell me about your

00:14:24.150 --> 00:14:24.160
day.'That's

00:14:24.160 --> 00:14:26.470
communion. That's fellowship. And that was

00:14:26.480 --> 00:14:28.629
whenever we were seeing them walking, not

00:14:28.629 --> 00:14:28.639
like

00:14:28.639 --> 00:14:30.629
whenever you see

00:14:30.639 --> 00:14:32.470
the sand on the beach and he says,

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:34.150
'Well, where are my footprints?

00:14:34.160 --> 00:14:36.230
That's when I was carrying

00:14:36.230 --> 00:14:36.240
you.'We

00:14:36.240 --> 00:14:39.110
were walking beside him and we were

00:14:39.120 --> 00:14:41.590
making indentations in the spirit

00:14:41.600 --> 00:14:45.189
realm as we were walking with footprints

00:14:45.199 --> 00:14:47.910
like it is in the snow. And I saw an

00:14:47.910 --> 00:14:47.920
indentation

00:14:47.920 --> 00:14:50.550
of the glory as we were

00:14:50.560 --> 00:14:54.230
pushing in the glory with the Father.

00:14:54.240 --> 00:14:56.470
As he is, so are we in this world, and

00:14:56.480 --> 00:14:59.189
we were walking side by side with him in

00:14:59.199 --> 00:15:01.590
the spirit realm. And that's what he

00:15:01.600 --> 00:15:04.150
said: 'This is a higher level of

00:15:04.160 --> 00:15:06.470
prayer.'As

00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:08.949
I was praying today, I saw us trying—He said, 'Come up! Come up to the throne. Come up higher.'And there were things trying to grab ahold of us to pull us down. They were grabbing ahold of our feet, trying to pull you out of those cloud banks. He said, 'Come up above it. Come up above the clouds. Kick

00:15:08.949 --> 00:15:08.959
those things off that try to hold you back, son.'He was talking to me and Diana. 'Kick those things, the pricks, the things that come against you. Come up to the throne of God.'As I was driving,

00:15:08.959 --> 00:15:11.030
he said, 'Come up, come up,

00:15:27.279 --> 00:15:30.069
son.

00:15:35.839 --> 00:15:37.670
You've

00:15:41.680 --> 00:15:44.389
got to kick those things off.

00:15:44.399 --> 00:15:45.750
They're trying to grab ahold of your

00:15:45.760 --> 00:15:48.310
feet. Don't allow them.'So I say that

00:15:48.320 --> 00:15:51.430
to you. Don't allow the things of this

00:15:51.440 --> 00:15:53.590
world to hold your feet down. Come up

00:15:53.600 --> 00:15:56.230
higher into the throne of God. Come up

00:15:56.240 --> 00:15:58.790
higher above the clouds. It's

00:15:58.800 --> 00:16:01.269
time to soar like the eagles in these

00:16:01.279 --> 00:16:03.670
last days. But things of this

00:16:03.670 --> 00:16:03.680
world—emails

00:16:03.680 --> 00:16:06.069
or whatever you

00:16:06.079 --> 00:16:08.389
might face during the day—try to

00:16:08.399 --> 00:16:11.350
hold your feet down. They try to hold

00:16:11.360 --> 00:16:14.310
you back. Life circumstances,

00:16:14.320 --> 00:16:16.550
ailments with your flesh,

00:16:16.560 --> 00:16:18.470
financial

00:16:18.470 --> 00:16:18.480
pressure—you

00:16:18.480 --> 00:16:22.230
name it—try to hold

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:24.790
you down because it's carnal thinking.

00:16:24.800 --> 00:16:27.350
It tries to get you to think carnally,

00:16:27.360 --> 00:16:29.910
but you've got to come up higher and

00:16:29.920 --> 00:16:33.030
renew your mind by the word of God. And

00:16:33.030 --> 00:16:33.040
he

00:16:33.040 --> 00:16:34.389
said, 'Come up, come

00:16:34.389 --> 00:16:34.399
up.'And

00:16:34.399 --> 00:16:36.629
as I was driving, I could

00:16:36.639 --> 00:16:38.310
see the little things trying to latch

00:16:38.310 --> 00:16:38.320
onto

00:16:38.320 --> 00:16:40.069
the heel of my foot, trying to pull

00:16:40.079 --> 00:16:41.749
me down out of that cloud bank

00:16:41.759 --> 00:16:44.069
with life circumstances. But he said,

00:16:44.079 --> 00:16:47.110
'You must kick them off and fly above

00:16:47.120 --> 00:16:48.949
it,

00:16:48.959 --> 00:16:50.710
for I've called you to soar like an

00:16:50.720 --> 00:16:54.069
eagle.

00:16:54.079 --> 00:16:56.710
Yield to the anointing that I've put

00:16:56.720 --> 00:16:59.189
upon your life.'Say it right now: I

00:16:59.199 --> 00:17:01.990
yield to the anointing that God has

00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:03.829
placed on my life. I yield to it.

00:17:03.839 --> 00:17:05.909
I don't put a wall up

00:17:05.919 --> 00:17:08.710
toward it anymore. I'm yielded to what

00:17:08.720 --> 00:17:10.710
God has for me.

00:17:10.720 --> 00:17:15.429
I surrender all to what God has for me.

00:17:15.439 --> 00:17:18.069
That's what you've got to do. I surrender

00:17:18.079 --> 00:17:20.789
to the prophetic. I surrender to the

00:17:20.799 --> 00:17:23.590
watchman call. I surrender to the

00:17:23.600 --> 00:17:25.669
healing manifestations flowing through

00:17:25.679 --> 00:17:30.310
me. Don't be a wall; be a river that

00:17:30.320 --> 00:17:34.310
lets the Holy Spirit flow through you.

00:17:34.320 --> 00:17:36.230
So that whenever you are in those

00:17:36.240 --> 00:17:39.270
circumstances of life and the storms are

00:17:39.280 --> 00:17:41.029
blowing, it doesn't

00:17:41.039 --> 00:17:42.870
bother you because I'm soaring

00:17:42.880 --> 00:17:47.510
above the storm.

00:17:47.520 --> 00:17:49.110
I'm coming up higher in prayer. I'm

00:17:49.120 --> 00:17:50.710
coming up higher with my fellowship with

00:17:50.720 --> 00:17:53.669
him. And I saw them keep trying to pull

00:17:53.679 --> 00:17:55.830
me

00:17:55.830 --> 00:17:55.840
down—demonic

00:17:55.840 --> 00:17:57.830
forces, things try to pull you

00:17:57.840 --> 00:18:00.150
out of that cloud bank.

00:18:00.160 --> 00:18:02.390
'Oh well, they said

00:18:02.400 --> 00:18:04.470
this about you. Oh well, this happened

00:18:04.480 --> 00:18:06.630
to you. Oh well, you've got this

00:18:06.630 --> 00:18:06.640
going.'And

00:18:06.640 --> 00:18:08.630
they try to pull you out of that. I'm

00:18:08.640 --> 00:18:11.669
going to remain focused, going vertical

00:18:11.679 --> 00:18:13.990
and not horizontal. I'm staying vertical

00:18:14.000 --> 00:18:16.710
on him tonight.

00:18:16.720 --> 00:18:17.990
And that's what you've got to do. I'm

00:18:18.000 --> 00:18:19.510
trying to tell you all

00:18:19.520 --> 00:18:22.070
what I try to do. 'Well, didn't you see

00:18:22.080 --> 00:18:23.990
this? Didn't you see?'I don't care.

00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:26.390
I'm staying vertical.

00:18:26.400 --> 00:18:29.510
I'm staying with him far above all

00:18:29.520 --> 00:18:32.230
principalities and powers according to

00:18:32.240 --> 00:18:34.070
Ephesians.

00:18:34.080 --> 00:18:36.630
I believe, Father, that you've made a

00:18:36.640 --> 00:18:40.950
way for me. No matter how much I kick

00:18:40.960 --> 00:18:44.470
these things off, I refuse to allow

00:18:44.480 --> 00:18:48.230
strife in. I refuse to allow people

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:50.950
to be a Debbie Downer in my life. I'm

00:18:50.960 --> 00:18:55.110
not going to have Debbie Downers,

00:18:55.120 --> 00:18:56.789
Brandon. 'Well, you say a lot of things

00:18:56.799 --> 00:18:58.230
that are hard and there seem to be

00:18:58.240 --> 00:19:01.190
Debbie Downer.'I'm not a Debbie Downer.

00:19:01.200 --> 00:19:03.990
I'm trying to tell you what I'm

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:05.990
seeing by the spirit of God as I'm

00:19:06.000 --> 00:19:08.630
flying above and looking across the edge

00:19:08.640 --> 00:19:11.029
of the horizon of time. Say, 'Hey, if you

00:19:11.039 --> 00:19:13.110
come on board and we pray for this, we

00:19:13.120 --> 00:19:15.750
can change

00:19:15.750 --> 00:19:15.760
this.'I'm

00:19:15.760 --> 00:19:18.470
holding the church accountable.

00:19:18.480 --> 00:19:20.230
What happens in America and what happens

00:19:20.240 --> 00:19:23.110
in these places is up to the church.

00:19:23.120 --> 00:19:27.510
Take your authority, church. Take your

00:19:27.520 --> 00:19:30.070
authority. I'm not going to do

00:19:30.080 --> 00:19:33.029
anything else about the devil; I've

00:19:33.039 --> 00:19:35.909
already done it all. I said, 'It is

00:19:35.919 --> 00:19:39.909
finished.'Do

00:19:39.919 --> 00:19:41.830
you ever remember Brother

00:19:41.830 --> 00:19:41.840
Hagin

00:19:41.840 --> 00:19:44.150
talking about the

00:19:44.160 --> 00:19:45.669
encounter he had with Jesus? Listen,

00:19:45.669 --> 00:19:45.679
I've

00:19:45.679 --> 00:19:47.669
got to be

00:19:47.679 --> 00:19:50.549
quick; I'm talking too much.

00:19:50.559 --> 00:19:52.789
The devil was there, and

00:19:52.799 --> 00:19:54.630
this devil was flapping his hands.

00:19:54.640 --> 00:19:55.990
If you go back and hear the 'Authority of

00:19:56.000 --> 00:19:57.669
the

00:19:57.669 --> 00:19:57.679
Believer'sermon

00:19:57.679 --> 00:19:59.270
series he had—he had a

00:19:59.280 --> 00:20:01.430
visitation from the Lord and was

00:20:01.430 --> 00:20:01.440
talking—all

00:20:01.440 --> 00:20:04.310
of a sudden this devil

00:20:04.320 --> 00:20:06.390
came out and started

00:20:06.390 --> 00:20:06.400
making

00:20:06.400 --> 00:20:10.070
noise.

00:20:10.080 --> 00:20:13.350
He was so frustrated because

00:20:13.360 --> 00:20:15.430
Jesus wouldn't do anything about the

00:20:15.440 --> 00:20:17.750
devil

00:20:17.760 --> 00:20:19.669
and he couldn't hear what the

00:20:19.679 --> 00:20:22.150
Lord was saying because the devil was

00:20:22.160 --> 00:20:24.310
making such a loud noise by his feet.

00:20:24.320 --> 00:20:26.789
He was

00:20:26.799 --> 00:20:29.430
like, 'Oh, I wish the Lord would do

00:20:29.440 --> 00:20:31.590
something about this

00:20:31.590 --> 00:20:31.600
devil.'Jesus

00:20:31.600 --> 00:20:33.430
was talking the whole time and he

00:20:33.440 --> 00:20:34.710
couldn't hear anything He was saying

00:20:34.720 --> 00:20:36.950
because He wouldn't take care of

00:20:36.960 --> 00:20:39.430
that devil for him. So, Brother

00:20:39.430 --> 00:20:39.440
Hagin

00:20:39.440 --> 00:20:41.510
said in the vision, 'In the name

00:20:41.520 --> 00:20:43.990
of Jesus, devil, get out of here! Shut

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:45.990
up and

00:20:45.990 --> 00:20:46.000
go!'That

00:20:46.000 --> 00:20:47.669
devil took off and got out of there.

00:20:47.679 --> 00:20:49.350
He said, 'Why didn't You do anything

00:20:49.360 --> 00:20:50.710
about it?'Jesus said, 'I couldn't do

00:20:50.720 --> 00:20:51.990
anything about it.'He said, 'What do

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:53.430
you mean You couldn't?'He said,

00:20:58.400 --> 00:21:00.630
'I don't think I heard You correctly,'and

00:21:00.630 --> 00:21:00.640
they

00:21:00.640 --> 00:21:02.310
kept arguing back and

00:21:02.320 --> 00:21:05.110
forth. Basically, the bottom line is if he

00:21:05.120 --> 00:21:07.590
wouldn't take his authority and tell

00:21:07.600 --> 00:21:09.990
that devil to get out of

00:21:09.990 --> 00:21:10.000
here—Jesus

00:21:10.000 --> 00:21:12.549
already did it, and it

00:21:12.559 --> 00:21:16.230
took us to do it. The bottom line

00:21:17.440 --> 00:21:19.590
is that Christ

00:21:19.600 --> 00:21:22.149
gave you authority over the devil, and

00:21:22.159 --> 00:21:24.230
Jesus is not going to do any more about

00:21:24.240 --> 00:21:26.390
the devil. You're going to have to stand

00:21:26.400 --> 00:21:27.909
up against him with the sword of the

00:21:27.909 --> 00:21:27.919
Spirit

00:21:27.919 --> 00:21:30.870
and tell him, as James 4:7

00:21:30.870 --> 00:21:30.880
says,

00:21:30.880 --> 00:21:32.710
'Submit yourself

00:21:32.720 --> 00:21:35.750
therefore unto God, resist the devil and

00:21:35.760 --> 00:21:38.950
he will flee.'If you

00:21:38.960 --> 00:21:40.789
don't do that, he's going to sit there

00:21:40.799 --> 00:21:43.270
and nip at your feet.

00:21:43.280 --> 00:21:45.110
That's why I tell you all the time

00:21:45.120 --> 00:21:47.909
to take

00:21:47.919 --> 00:21:49.590
your authority. That's why I have Sister

00:21:49.590 --> 00:21:49.600
Billye's

00:21:49.600 --> 00:21:51.350
books and we keep them all

00:21:51.360 --> 00:21:52.950
around. I've got them everywhere so

00:21:52.960 --> 00:21:55.029
that you understand the power of the

00:21:55.039 --> 00:21:56.390
authority of the believer.

00:22:00.080 --> 00:22:02.870
It's important because the Lord's

00:22:02.880 --> 00:22:04.230
not going to do anything else about the

00:22:04.240 --> 00:22:06.470
devil. He gave you power and authority

00:22:06.480 --> 00:22:08.630
to tread on serpents and scorpions and

00:22:08.640 --> 00:22:11.029
nothing shall by any means hurt you. Is

00:22:11.039 --> 00:22:13.029
that literal? I believe it's

00:22:13.039 --> 00:22:15.669
literal and

00:22:16.880 --> 00:22:18.149
metaphorical.

00:22:19.919 --> 00:22:22.470
I believe that Jesus

00:22:22.480 --> 00:22:24.789
gave me power and authority over the

00:22:24.799 --> 00:22:27.029
principalities and all of it

00:22:27.039 --> 00:22:28.789
concerning me and my house. I don't go

00:22:28.799 --> 00:22:30.789
around binding everything else out here

00:22:30.789 --> 00:22:30.799
or

00:22:30.799 --> 00:22:32.390
going into neighborhoods

00:22:32.390 --> 00:22:32.400
binding

00:22:32.400 --> 00:22:34.950
the devil and the principality over

00:22:34.960 --> 00:22:37.430
Tulsa. No,

00:22:37.440 --> 00:22:40.470
concerning me and my house, you

00:22:40.480 --> 00:22:42.789
have no power in my house.

00:22:42.799 --> 00:22:44.870
I pray over my

00:22:44.880 --> 00:22:46.630
president and my

00:22:46.640 --> 00:22:48.310
neighborhood, but I don't go to your

00:22:48.320 --> 00:22:49.590
house and start binding the

00:22:49.600 --> 00:22:52.549
principality of Persia and

00:22:52.559 --> 00:22:56.230
being stupid. I take authority over my

00:22:56.240 --> 00:22:59.430
house, my children, my wife,

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:03.430
my finances, and my church. I pray

00:23:03.440 --> 00:23:06.470
over my pastors and our leaders,

00:23:06.480 --> 00:23:08.390
that You give them fresh revelation

00:23:08.400 --> 00:23:11.510
knowledge to teach the body of Christ.

00:23:11.520 --> 00:23:13.750
We pray over

00:23:13.760 --> 00:23:17.270
our leaders

00:23:17.280 --> 00:23:19.350
and we flow in that gift.

00:23:23.760 --> 00:23:25.590
Lord said, 'Keep it shorter. Pray

00:23:25.600 --> 00:23:28.911
more.'Father,

00:23:28.921 --> 00:23:30.230
we

00:23:30.240 --> 00:23:32.149
thank You

00:23:32.159 --> 00:23:35.990
for the body.

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:37.669
We thank You, Lord, for all that You've

00:23:37.679 --> 00:23:39.590
done for us.

00:23:39.600 --> 00:23:41.510
We thank You that by Your stripes we

00:23:41.510 --> 00:23:41.520
are

00:23:41.520 --> 00:23:44.710
healed. We're so grateful for

00:23:44.720 --> 00:23:46.870
tongues and the interpretation of tongues.

00:23:46.880 --> 00:23:48.870
We're so grateful for the gifts of the

00:23:48.880 --> 00:23:51.430
Spirit, that we walk in divine healing

00:23:51.430 --> 00:23:51.440
and

00:23:51.440 --> 00:23:53.909
health. We walk in the

00:23:53.919 --> 00:23:56.630
authority of the believer

00:23:56.640 --> 00:23:58.870
and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

